input: Subject: A serene tea ceremony; Characteristics: traditional Japanese tea set and tatami mats; Timing and lighting: afternoon with natural light; Background: minimalist room with sliding doors; Feeling: peaceful and mindful.
output: Capture a serene scene of a traditional Japanese tea ceremony unfolding on a sun-drenched afternoon. A weathered wooden tea set sits elegantly upon the woven tatami mats, bathed in soft, warm natural light streaming through minimalist sliding doors. Wisps of incense curl gently in the stillness of the room, hinting at a quiet contemplation and inviting a sense of peaceful mindfulness.
